snippet.title: lacey's flash games DEMO - announcement trailer
snippet.description:
demo out february 28th on steam and itch.io..
Wishlist now here!: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3459340/Laceys_Flash_Games/
based off and continuing the story of the digital horror youtube series. 
created by ghosttundra in partnership with brand new groove and euroclipse studio.

também estará disponível em pt-br!
